text: Diane Crespo is a producer and director of feature films and documentaries. She co-founded Cicala Filmworks in 1997. Her film credits include Arranged (director/producer), Clutter (director), My Last Day Without You (producer) and Contested Streets (producer). == References == ==External links== * *Cicala Filmworks Category:American film producers Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people
